summary:
Mix of different ENB presets making the already beautiful Skyrim look even more fantastic!
Give it a try, it doesn\'t cost anything ;)
descriptionHtml:
[IMG]http://i1122.photobucket.com/albums/l527/hinti21/Skyrim/ENBMix%201-03/enb2.jpg[/IMG]

Here you can look at my photobucket-album (where I upload pictures of this ENBMix):
http://s1122.photobucket.com/albums/l527/hinti21/Skyrim/ENBMix%201-03/

Here some comparison-shots, so you know what you\'ll be dealing with ;)
[IMG]http://i1122.photobucket.com/albums/l527/hinti21/Skyrim/ENBMix%201-03/Comparison-shots/mini1.gif[/IMG]
[IMG]http://i1122.photobucket.com/albums/l527/hinti21/Skyrim/ENBMix%201-03/Comparison-shots/mini4.gif[/IMG]
[IMG]http://i1122.photobucket.com/albums/l527/hinti21/Skyrim/ENBMix%201-03/Comparison-shots/mini2.gif[/IMG]
[IMG]http://i1122.photobucket.com/albums/l527/hinti21/Skyrim/ENBMix%201-03/Comparison-shots/mini3.gif[/IMG]

This is NOT my mod, it\'s just a mix of different settings with a little tweaking by myself!

The base of this mod was created by Boris Vorontsov.
Many people tweaked it and I picked out what I found best
from superl3, TheRadikal, HeliosDoubleSix, yoon2886 and 
Matso, played around with the .ini a bit and put it together
in this ENB mix.

Thanks to all of you guys for making gaming a whole new experience!!

BTW: I use Realistic Lighting (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=7654), which is already included in the download, and a load of texture- and other mods (STEP -> http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=11).
author: hinti21
